---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 mb-8">
    <div class="flex-1">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About</h1>
      
      <p class="mb-4">
        Starting as an intern at Backbone PLM, I immersed myself in web development alongside my traditional CS education. 
        Now I'm a full stack engineer at Bamboo Rose, the parent company of Backbone PLM, since graduating from CSU in May 2023.
      </p>
      
      <p class="mb-4">
        Outside of work, I enjoy a variety of hobbies. I play drums for Avalanche and Nuggets games, love to rock climb, 
        golf, ski, and hike.
      </p>
      
      <p class="mb-6">
        I'm always striving to improve my skills and learn new things. I pride myself on being a natural leader, learning 
        new things extremely quickly, and communicating effectively.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <img 
      src="/daniel.jpg" 
      alt="Daniel Ives" 
      loading="lazy"
      class="w-48 md:w-64 aspect-[2/3] rounded-lg object-cover object-top flex-shrink-0"
      style="object-position: top 20%;"
    />
  </div>
  
  <p>
    <a href="/">‚Üê Back to home</a>
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
